{"tid":2045942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地澳門抵港人士強制檢疫周日屆滿 食衞局：三地傾向逐步放寬","createTime":"2020-06-01T06:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T06:09:47.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67ea10adc95ea341c100a1027a6b44822d14dac2","tid":2045942,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:03:50.000Z","msg":"內地澳門抵港人士強制檢疫周日屆滿 食衞局：三地傾向逐步放寬<br />\n1小時前<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】內地和澳門抵港人士強制檢疫措施周日屆滿，食物及衞生局指三地政府傾向逐步有序地放寬，又透露正在研究類似內地的健康碼，在本港協助控制疫情。<br />\n<br />\n本港再出現新冠病毒本地感染個案，其中一名患者在物流公司負責標籤進口包裝蔬果。有立法會議員向政府提出，對供港食品進行病毒測試，食物及衞生局副秘書長陳偉基表示，此項工作非常龐大，而目前未有專家作出類似建議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392899&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGhdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=74abcfd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392899&h=ef1af3df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392899</a>"},{"pid":"8447a35dd243a765364d049f6fcea8457115a67a","tid":2045942,"uid":326881,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"屌，應該延遲個強制檢疫Lor"},{"pid":"f6565fcb315e6f014bc60c020d42ad07ad84a37d","tid":2045942,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"研究類似內地的健康碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsocial credit system"}]}